---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="About Mind Success Program | Our Mission to Transform Mindsets"
  description="Learn about Mind Success Program — a dedicated platform helping people discover the world's best mindset tools, programs, and techniques for personal transformation."
  ogImage="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522202176988-66273c2fd55f?w=1200"
>
  <section class="relative py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0D0D1A] via-[#1A1A2E] to-[#0D0D1A]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Our <span class="text-[#D4AF37]">Mission</span></h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        Mind Success Program is a dedicated resource for people who want to unlock the full potential of their minds — and build lives of genuine, lasting success.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-[#0D0D1A]">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-20">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Why We Exist</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            The personal development industry is massive — and overwhelming. There are thousands of programs, books, courses, and coaches promising transformation. But how do you know which ones actually work?
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            That's why we built Mind Success Program. We research, review, and curate only the highest-quality mindset programs and resources available — so you can spend less time searching and more time growing.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            Every recommendation on this site is evaluated on its scientific backing, real-world effectiveness, quality of instruction, and overall value. We only share what we'd genuinely recommend.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522202176988-66273c2fd55f?w=800&q=80"
            alt="Team collaborating on personal development research"
            class="w-full h-80 object-cover"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-20">
        <div class="bg-[#1A1A2E] rounded-2xl p-8 text-center border border-[#D4AF37]/20">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🎯</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Honest Reviews</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">We give unbiased, in-depth reviews of every program — the good, the bad, and the honest truth.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[#1A1A2E] rounded-2xl p-8 text-center border border-[#D4AF37]/20">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🧠</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Science-Backed</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">We prioritize content rooted in neuroscience, psychology, and proven behavior change research.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[#1A1A2E] rounded-2xl p-8 text-center border border-[#D4AF37]/20">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🚀</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Results-Focused</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">Everything we cover is focused on one thing: helping you get real, measurable results in your life.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#D4AF37]/20 to-[#7C3AED]/20 rounded-2xl p-10 text-center border border-[#D4AF37]/30">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Our Promise to You</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          We will always be transparent about our recommendations. Some links on this site are affiliate links — meaning we may earn a commission if you purchase through them, at no extra cost to you. This helps us keep the site free and keep producing quality content.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#D4AF37] font-semibold mt-4">We only recommend what we genuinely believe in.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
